<p>"<span style="color:#252C2F;"><span style="font-family:Helvetica;"><span style="font-size:13px;">just seeing the suggestion...could cause people to take a look...the bare act is all of it...[with] no need even to link it with any results" is John Sherman's comment about just one look. It cannot be stated more simply. After looking at me you are left with your life. Ain't it grand even when it is painful or not.</span></span></span></p>
